&lt;p&gt;An exciting secondment opportunity has arisen in the Asthma &amp; Allergy Department for an experienced clinical member of staff with demonstrable administrative skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This unique post will include clinical duties, supporting the smooth running of clinics as well as booking clinics and managing e-referrals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Youwill oversee the Asthma &amp; Allergy administration team andwill be instrumental in exploring a joined up paediatric booking function.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you would like an informal chat about the role please contact christine.townshend2@nhs.net.&lt;/p&gt;
